{"tid":392184,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"唉就黎同老母去旅行點算","createTime":"2017-09-08T10:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T10:07:30.000Z","uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26623fdd6de32d3a30f67ce28b14120e87dfad31","tid":392184,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:34:00.000Z","msg":"去日本佢話唔食魚蝦蟹，食菜咁話wo...<br />\n<br />\n去呢就吸收上次既教訓 ，已經plan到冇咁趕，費時搵路搭車又煩，行又話攰<br />\n<br />\n同埋去遠既地方好醒咁報左個local tour(唔知成團未）唔撚洗煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n住就由於上次住airbnb貪平又難搵又細間，今次好醒咁搵apa 夠抵吊又住得下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搭車就預撚晒早幾粒鐘去，上次走同去都差d趕唔到班機嚇到仆街，佢話8點開咪8點先到咪得....<br />\n<br />\n但係食真係好撚難搞 邊撚到搵條菜俾佢食，唔通叫個日本仔烚條菜心俾佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36031d7ca0450b6fede2a9a806e153c32f76eb5a","tid":392184,"uid":17637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:39:08.000Z","msg":"打巴佢"},{"pid":"e12a81f6808a4bfd63482e835f1eecbda5b287ac","tid":392184,"uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:41:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打巴佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未講重點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大部分都係我俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164a6f63a21f05c722cd26383e3e83e9c4ff1a37","tid":392184,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:03:07.000Z","msg":"點都要開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女可以一街都係<br />\n老媽子得一個"},{"pid":"17b88741fc61d19ee3e29ba56b2529d334a87a99","tid":392184,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點都要開心呀<img src=\"/assets